libtensorflowlite_c.so for 32-bit ARM (armv7l / armhf).
TensorFlow Lite C v2.17.1 (matches the other platforms from tphakala/tflite_c).
Built for armv7-a + neon-vfpv4 (Cortex-A7) via Docker/QEMU; see the PR for the
reproducible build script. tphakala/tflite_c does not publish an armv7l release,
so this lib is supplied here directly.
